org.apache.poi.xddf.usermodel.chart

Class XDDFDateAxis

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.xddf.usermodel.chart.XDDFChartAxis
      • org.apache.poi.xddf.usermodel.chart.XDDFDateAxis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasShapeProperties 

    @Beta
public class XDDFDateAxis
extends XDDFChartAxis
    Date axis type. Currently only implements the same values as XDDFCategoryAxis, since the two are nearly identical.(日期轴类型。目前仅实现与XDDFcategoryAx相同的值，因为两者几乎相同。)
